Package: bocvaletR
Title: Bank of Canada Valet API R Interface
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    c(
        person("Zihao", "Sheng",email = "1844716292@qq.com",role = c("aut", "cre")),
        person("Wei", "Li", role = "aut"),
        person("Inaara", "Rajwani", role = "aut")
    )
Depends: R (>= 4.1.0)
Description: Provides a tidy R interface to the Bank of Canada Valet API for
    discovering series and groups, retrieving time series observations, and
    monitoring foreign exchange updates via the FX RSS feed. Includes helper
    functions for preprocessing and summary tasks such as filling missing
    values, normalization, returns, rolling smoothing, and correlation
    diagnostics.
